    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**1.研究背景**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**行为识别是什么**",
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**行为识别是什么**",
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/41ded1b7eb9e56f2b30c30a7972fadad019f35f88f9aecdbc6ce08e397ce7ca6.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**行为识别流程**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/319460d631cf01196d2ffe087289fef34938df7e95eb9a088d58a1ae54753bb7.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "GCN",
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "Segmentation（分段 / 窗口分割）Scaling（归一化 / 标准化）Whitening（白化）RBM（受限玻尔兹曼机）AE（自编码器）",
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**基于骨模态行为识别流程**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/2a5666d7d6260ec196ccaa039cb3200b47bea116f6f23aabc9d658f4de47e591.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**为什么用骨模态做行为识别**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**计算效率高**",
        "text_level": 3,
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**环境鲁棒性强**",
        "text_level": 3,
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**隐私风险低**",
        "text_level": 3,
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "相比 RGB、光流等模态，骨架数据的计算成本更低，处理起来更高效",
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "受复杂环境、视角变化、身体尺度、运动速度变化的影响更小，识别稳定性更好",
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "骨架数据不会暴露用户的外貌细节，减少了隐私泄露的顾虑",
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "需要预处理：骨骼提取算法，包括目标检测和姿态估计",
        "page_idx": 6
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**2.相关工作**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**骨模态行为识别工作流**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/4105087ff1069aba091e428194b0ca9aaa8f38d3dcf346810783285ea6a6343a.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "骨架数据→多模态拆分→数据增强→格式转换→特征提取→时空建模→输出动作类别",
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "Skeletal Data Modalities（骨架数据模态）Geometric Features（几何特征）Generalized Features（泛化特征）",
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "Sequential （序列表示）Pseudo-Image （伪图像表示）Token-Based（基于 Token 的表示Transformer）",
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "空间特征提取单帧内的关节关系，比如用 GCN ；时间特征提取处理帧与帧之间的变化，比如用 CNN、RNN",
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "串行、并行、融合",
        "page_idx": 8
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**骨模态行为识别特征提取**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/8891571a7a01ec267517094a4a05d795e6753b469d71c1028c8f9e880102982c.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "CNN 骨架数据构建为伪图像利用卷积提取时空特征",
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "RNN 骨架视作时序序列循环结构建模动作动态变化",
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "GCN 人体拓扑图结构通过图卷积挖掘关节时空关联",
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Transformer 骨架转为 Token 依靠自注意力机制捕捉全局远距离依赖",
        "page_idx": 9
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**骨模态行为识别发展时间线**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "BlockGCN",
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/c25b0501ff02cb80bcec2b24c7a675ed188a21fe9279a3090f2b330196d19d3e.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "包括：RNN、CNN、 GCN、Transformer、生成式、混合等方法",
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "RNN、CNN难以显式捕捉关节间的空间关联",
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因此后续研究趋势转向 GCN、Transformer 等方法",
        "page_idx": 10
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**GCN 骨模态行为识别研究现状**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**邻接矩阵**",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**相对位置编码**",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**多关系建模**",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "固定拓扑：基于骨骼物理连接定义固定的邻接矩阵",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "可学习拓扑：捕捉物理连接和非连接关节间的关系",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "存在\"灾难性遗忘\"问题：骨骼拓扑信息在训练中逐渐被侵蚀",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "在 NLP 和 CV 被证明有效",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "对图数据上的Transformer模型有益",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "但在骨架动作识别领域探索不充分",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "每层并行使用多个GC",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "引入注意力机制调整连接权重",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "计算开销大，参数量大，低效",
        "page_idx": 11
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**3.现存问题**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 12
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**GCN 问题一：“灾难性遗忘”**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 13
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/8cfc743543cdbc6ea2c381c0756948773ee5f3cad8b2b1457c002f33ed6ac26c.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 13
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "训练前初始化的是符合人体物理结构的骨骼拓扑，但训练结束后，原始的骨骼连接性没有被保留下来，即“灾难性遗忘”",
        "page_idx": 13
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**GCN 问题二：“低效多关系建模”**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 14
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/dc120d4b87f5b89518a20f8da9e2bfbbbfd94092812db95a1c9208716785f976.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 14
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "“低效多关系建模”：参数和计算量大，权重矩阵存在大量冗余",
        "page_idx": 14
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**4.研究方法**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 15
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**BlockGC 模块**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 16
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/ab32f923567445a166a58c46f1187a7633921ebec35cbce2ba480ecf636db483.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 16
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "包括拓扑编码（保留骨架结构信息）和分块对角卷积（降低参数量）",
        "page_idx": 16
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "上图是动态编码，下图是静态编码",
        "page_idx": 16
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**静态拓扑编码**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 17
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/7964f8e3a6964325508cbd687fc36ced5bd4ca8b060cb4e8e5d899f629b00118.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 17
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/3ec61439564d586a6b59e98c9ae8b6cf2e17a87e28454382b124cc870af122c8.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 17
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "采用骨骼最短路径距离（SPD），通过嵌入表转换成可学习的特征向量，构建出静态拓扑编码矩阵 B，保留物理连接",
        "page_idx": 17
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**动态拓扑编码**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/a43f96b27a41eae4030f8ac99a64d4ece92412ccd2d58a400e4a1612f83a89ca.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "基于关节间欧氏距离构建骨架的过滤序列，提取出随动作变化的拓扑条形码，再通过向量化和投影，得到动作特有的动态拓扑特征",
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "w 是关节 i 和 j 在 3D 空间中的实际欧氏距离，会随着每一帧的姿态变化而变化",
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "计算单帧图片",
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "举例：抬手时，手和头的w会变小；放下时，w 会变大。",
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "初始状态K1：所有关节都是孤立的点，没有任何连接；都活着，所以蓝线都有",
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "逐渐增大距离阈值，当 阈值大于某对关节的距离 w 时，就把这两个关节连起来，从属端死亡，蓝线终止",
        "page_idx": 18
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**动态拓扑编码**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 19
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "梳头",
        "page_idx": 19
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "握手",
        "page_idx": 19
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/7f9f3f3d628a804751ca9f48c5a5beea84a3c0ff189dea86b4cb5dc2f77cba83.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 19
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "各组样本呈现出明显的类间差异、类内相似特性",
        "page_idx": 19
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "同一个动作，一组三个样本",
        "page_idx": 19
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**分块对角卷积**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 20
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/27fffb4829180b007f4b23231959ea7a0cd91971060e14f4f044ac6e3f445690.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 20
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/7d82fdabe0a3925c935185f6a9cc92300fb13df7a668fba3c011a4a04d44a9ce.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 20
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Ensemble of GCs：最朴素的多关系方法，直接堆叠 K 个完全独立的 GC 层",
        "page_idx": 20
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Proposed BlockGC：K 个邻接矩阵 + K 个独立的分块对角权重矩阵",
        "page_idx": 20
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/4600c763053bf9106dd7342e574b668a9def1630e106a082b5113688d34f03d9.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 20
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "同一个动作，一组三个样本",
        "page_idx": 20
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "参数量是 \"模型有多大\"，决定了你需要多少硬盘存它，多少显存加载它",
        "page_idx": 20
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "计算量是 \"模型跑一次要做多少运算\"，决定了你训练它要花多久，推理它有多快",
        "page_idx": 20
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**分块对角卷积推导**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 21
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/449ddc31a5487954037e706becb2ef5fb03b363b09529b9a2d4cea0bdd409048.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 21
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "同一个动作，一组三个样本",
        "page_idx": 21
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "参数量是 \"模型有多大\"，决定了你需要多少硬盘存它，多少显存加载它",
        "page_idx": 21
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "计算量是 \"模型跑一次要做多少运算\"，决定了你训练它要花多久，推理它有多快",
        "page_idx": 21
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**分块对角卷积优势**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 22
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/108c05f195ddab39882d5ddcc3d69bc0eeb615b09c24d650b81d8791d4ef0cd2.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 22
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "同一个动作，一组三个样本",
        "page_idx": 22
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "参数量是 \"模型有多大\"，决定了你需要多少硬盘存它，多少显存加载它",
        "page_idx": 22
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "计算量是 \"模型跑一次要做多少运算\"，决定了你训练它要花多久，推理它有多快",
        "page_idx": 22
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**BlockGCN 架构**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 23
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/e478da0a006819c4f1419de4bb8304d3548ac5369bd00661cc558ba04765d192.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 23
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "多帧骨架序列→BlockGC→多尺度时间卷积",
        "page_idx": 23
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "→全局平均池化→全连接层→Softmax",
        "page_idx": 23
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "GAP:把关节维度和时间维度的特征压缩，变成一个固定长度的向量，消除序列长度和关节数的影响",
        "page_idx": 23
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "Linear：把压缩后的特征映射到动作类别数的维度",
        "page_idx": 23
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "Softmax：把输出转换成概率分布，每个值代表对应动作类别的置信度，最终取概率最高的类别作为预测结果",
        "page_idx": 23
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**5.实验结果**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 24
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**对比实验**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 25
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/c77c181223e40921247e11ec52174c3ab6a540ed96bcbaee0c4fa761fb433518.png",
        "image_caption": [],
        "page_idx": 25
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "可见该方法不仅在性能上领先，而且在参数量和计算量上都具备优势",
        "page_idx": 25
    },
    {
        "type": "page_footnote",
        "text": "x-sub跨主体x-view跨视角；星号部分是使用了额外的监督，并且没有动作模态；Joint, Bone, Joint Motion, and Bone Motion关节骨骼、关节运动、骨骼运动",
        "page_idx": 25
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "**消融实验1**",
        "text_level": 2,
        "page_idx": 26
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
